Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 我到底還能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了改變那如狹隘庭園般的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還活不到人生的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗 相擁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在無意識中被刻上的經驗紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當站在懸崖邊的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.47,0:00:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦難抓住了我的手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到了自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往更加寬廣的領域\N往更深更大的某處
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝著無法預測的世界前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And lt's calling me again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.96,0:01:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中城市目視確認
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,規模不斷擴展，似乎要覆蓋住夏威夷上空了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些突然出現在空中的城市群
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.47,0:01:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不斷擴展就像是要包裹住整個地球一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.77,0:01:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前仍在不斷增殖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.64,0:01:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然地球聯合認為這些城市群為戰鬥性武器的可能性極低
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.27,0:01:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且發表了希望民眾遵守正常社會秩序的聲明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.44,0:02:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是倫敦、德黑蘭、上海等17座城市已經發生了暴動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.74,0:02:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後的事態…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.44,0:02:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼長時間不在，真是很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.57,0:02:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，大家都期待著司令官的歸來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.36,0:02:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼今天看起來這麼有精神啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.74,0:02:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，大家少廢話了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作，工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正面臨關鍵性的局面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫東大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.25,0:02:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次，我打算和神名一起吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:02:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目擊情報稱僅關西地區就超過了80個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「其中，MU族28個，構造物30…」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界開始重合了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.54,0:03:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.84,0:03:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在綜合衍射圖上顯示的這個自稱是MU族特使的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經確認為前國防部一佐——九鬼正義
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MU大戰爆發後不久就行蹤不明瞭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據後來的調查
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷疑他潛伏在絕對障壁內
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.85,0:03:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我們從時間的牢獄中解放出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.36,0:04:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對此我要對給予我們幫助的諸位表示感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外，我命令諸位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即解除武裝並且交出Xephon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給你們24小時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果拒絕以上要求…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位難免大難臨頭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是30分鐘前，摧毀中京地區的D-1影像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:23.34,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}中京：名古屋的別稱，相對於東京（江戶）、西京（京都）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個D-1的全長推測為2.6公里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,質量為10的9次方噸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的破壞力為…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10的27次方爾格(erg)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:37.94,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}爾格(erg)：能量單位，1爾格相當於10的負7次方焦耳(J)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼恐怖的東西要來這裡啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題是包裹著RahXephon的這個卵形構造物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就所有的物理性接近方式對它都不奏效這點來看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它可能是一種不同的維度空間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在別說是啟動RahXephon了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是搬運它也很困難
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥力上的差距十分明顯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.75,0:05:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要怎麼辦啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然要戰鬥到底！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.84,0:05:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為，我們是TERRA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法接受！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為副司令我有權對\N這種魯莽的作戰計劃提出反對意見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧，少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是不會回心轉意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一點你最清楚吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樹！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是個不得要領的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此以外，別無它法…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對此我很羨慕…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你稍微替她想想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個和這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會保護她的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去保護吧，少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經想保護的就沒能…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狡猾…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狡猾…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狡猾！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離最後一班船出港還有1小時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還留在此處的市民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請按指定路線，立即到港口去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離最後一班船出港還有1小時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要這樣做？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是紮在我記憶中的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一根像刺一樣的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天必須要拔掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.94,0:06:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能邀請我來TERRA…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他興奮過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不是我而是他？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你的任務吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:07:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是olin的守護者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是yolteotl的見證者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…麻彌大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.06,0:08:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在做的事情真的是正確的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真正的正確的世界真的會來臨嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三輪，沒有什麼可擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做的事是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五味~呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的明天在哪裡啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問我！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了對岸，會讓我們下船是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，這艘船有它自己的船員呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，你和八雲君談過了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:08:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要好好談談啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡是個好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，是個好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管發生了很多事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟那裡曾經是我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次感到失去什麼了…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.66,0:09:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你身邊，默默注視著你的人，去在意她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直，只想著你一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.26,0:09:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:09:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是個好女人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.36,0:10:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-1確定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達第一級防衛線還有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10秒±20…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:10:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八雲司令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻象系統已經進入迎擊位置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你從這裡發佈指揮命令嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，是誰？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.96,0:11:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻象系統發射
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前正向D-1的航線飛去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航線修正，與敵人相遇還有20秒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是老樣子，賣命工作的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…17區，侵入藍色位置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旋風導彈迎擊發射準備
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻象4號，消失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第4小隊區支援第7區
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:11:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第1到第4區
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:11:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻象4號，消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第7區的防禦體制…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算是老友重逢了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀一尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.14,0:12:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，現在是TERRA的司令官大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殘存戰鬥力到60區集結
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指令確認
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.07,0:12:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到部下變得優秀了的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為上司，沒有比這更令我開心的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Delta陣型
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布奇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.67,0:12:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.26,0:12:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不還給我嗎？那隻貓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.56,0:12:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想聽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:12:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個身影…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旋風導彈的火力集中到D-1的下部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指令確認
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了現在你還敢頂撞我？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.06,0:13:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，這就叫「把別人的好心當成歹意」 …
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初下命令的是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，直接執行的人，卻是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.65,0:13:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的這雙手殺死了你女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.15,0:13:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全彈齊射！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:13:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的，功刀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是被稱為MU族的人們為了送走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與Xephon接觸的奏者而使用的通路…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏者？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是olin
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.36,0:14:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原先的olin們都從這裡通過…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊修特利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.16,0:14:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Xephon的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷失的olin如果在具有資格的年齡——17歲時找到我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那「真實」的「容顏」被認識為伊修特利(ixtli)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,olin成為「真實」的「心臟」——yolteotl進行調律
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調律什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並沒有希望你這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.27,0:14:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這不可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.27,0:14:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第3區被毀滅、第14區被毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第17區被毀滅…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果調律沒有完成就結束了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界就會變回成「泥之海」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是「真實」的「容顏」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不希望我存在，就無法…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別勉強了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經干的很不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了，無聊的餘興節目結束了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餘興節目現在剛剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一佐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jupiter系統啟動…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？ ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.75,0:17:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不會吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒聽說過有這種東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.34,0:17:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jupiter現象…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根來彼方幾乎全部被覆蓋了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.25,0:18:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.46,0:18:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:18:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jupiter現象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.57,0:19:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你思念的人，恐怕就在那裡面…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.24,0:19:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望我存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…看起來好像害怕著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.84,0:19:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來就像人類一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.77,0:19:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，我害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總在我身邊，保護著我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:20:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在，我有想去保護的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直沒有意識到…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.74,0:20:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,olin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.95,0:20:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是綾人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你一起活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起保護她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.55,0:20:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.98,0:20:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神由根源之地駕臨的島，根來島
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.15,0:20:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美麗的島
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.45,0:20:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人他？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.45,0:20:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.45,0:20:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.67,0:21:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的曲子是為誰彈的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.28,0:21:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向他告別…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.05,0:21:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就要回來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.18,0:21:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.85,0:23:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你，根據重疊的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.65,0:23:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道那個理由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.57,0:23:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.15,0:23:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集，第二十四樂章
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.74,0:23:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往調律的門
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.74,0:23:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界飽含著聲音